---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-20 border-t border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="container-wide py-12">
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-lg mb-3">
          <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-brand-600 text-white text-sm font-bold">AI</span>
          <span>SmartTools</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 max-w-md">
          Independent reviews & head-to-head comparisons of the best AI productivity and workflow tools in 2026. Tested, scored, ranked.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-500">
          <strong>Disclosure:</strong> Some links on this site are affiliate links. We may earn a commission when you sign up for a product we recommend, at no extra cost to you. This never influences our editorial scores.
          <a href="/disclosure" class="underline">Full disclosure →</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm text-slate-900 mb-3">Explore</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <li><a href="/best" class="hover:text-brand-600">Best-of Lists</a></li>
          <li><a href="/reviews" class="hover:text-brand-600">All Reviews</a></li>
          <li><a href="/compare" class="hover:text-brand-600">Comparisons</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides" class="hover:text-brand-600">Buying Guides</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm text-slate-900 mb-3">Company</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <li><a href="/about" class="hover:text-brand-600">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/disclosure" class="hover:text-brand-600">Affiliate Disclosure</a></li>
          <li><a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-brand-600">Privacy</a></li>
          <li><a href="mailto:hello@aismarttools.com" class="hover:text-brand-600">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-slate-200 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-xs text-slate-500">
      <p>© {year} AI Smart Tools. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>Made with Astro · Hosted on Cloudflare Pages</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
